From Seanna Watson Subject Re In article M Sheila Patterson writes As for the atheists agnostics who read this list if you aren't christian and if you have no intention of ever becoming one why on earth do you waste your time and mine by participating on a christian discussion list I find this remark to be awfully I would venture to say that there are many people who are Christians now who at one point in their lives had no intention of ever becoming a I was certainly one such I am quite thankful that there were Christians who were willing to continue to talk to me despite the appearance that it might have been a waste of their time and I even married one of be prepared to give an answer to everyone who asks you to give a reason for the hope that you But do this with gentleness and Peter Seanna Watson Bell Northern Research Pray that at the end of living Ottawa Ontario Canada Of philosophies and creeds God will find his people busy Opinion what opinions Oh these Planting trees and sowing No they're not BNR's they're I knew I'd left them Fred Kaan